by making you feel claustrophobic.

00:11.100 --> 00:13.000
Mm. It's growing pains, that's all.

00:13.000 --> 00:15.800
So, what time do you feel
you'll be going home?

00:15.700 --> 00:18.800
Andy was just telling me
he's joining the air force.

00:18.700 --> 00:22.600
He noticed my hair,
and detectives, they catch everything.

00:23.600 --> 00:25.500
Hey, Son.

00:25.500 --> 00:27.400
